1. --{ Welcome to the Quickstarter Guide!    In this chapter, you will find a mini version of the whole course. The goal is that you don't need more than this one chapter to jump right into the adventures of the Grünfeld Slav yourself. My goal was to equip you with 10% of the most important variations.    In making this selection, I used both master databases and the amateur database on Lichess to select the lines that you should statistically be confronted with most often.     Whenever I selected several lines from one chapter, I have usually tried to include both, variations that cover the basic ideas as well as those that represent the most theoretically critical continuations.     I hope that this mix will provide something for everyone and that you will feel ready to play your first games with the opening! }
