5. Nd5{ This is a very typical move in these lines with  Bf4 . We attack the bishop with tempo, are ready to go ... Nxc3  which will allow us to go  b7 - b5  and sometimes (especially after  a2 - a4 ) Black can put pressure on  c3  with moves like ... Bb4  and ... Qa5 . }
