10. Bd3( { The normal response.     A)  }10.Qb3?! { gives Black a lot of tempting options. Typical are }10...Na6 { or   }10...Nbd7 { to take on  c5  with tempo but even the concrete }10...Ne4! { puts White under a lot of pressure. For example }11.Ncxe4 dxe4! { followed by  ...Rd8  is annoying. } )( {  B)  }10.Qd1 { would be the best square for the queen but Black can just take on  c5  - either with or without taking on  c4  first. } )
