15. Bxa1{ This simple move seems best. White's pieces will be horribly misplaced, most notably the white king. }
16. Nxa1
16. Qxc4{ Keeping the king in the center while also a lot of White's pawns are hanging. ... Rfd8  is a huge threat.     With best play, White might hold this but I think practically, this is very tough to play. }
