14. Bd7{ Black protects  a4  and is now ready to play ... Qxd5  as well as ... Rac8 . }
15. O-O
15. Rac8{ I always enjoy moves that are more about positional domination than winning a pawn. Black paralyzes the  c3 -pawn before taking on  d5 . }( 15...Qxd5 { is also comfortable, but it just allows }16.c4 { when the c-pawn is a little bit more useful than on  c3 . } )
16. Rc1
