15. Na5{ White is a pawn up and has the bishop pair. But their king is a problem, ... Nb3  is coming and overall, Black just has nice control over the light squares on the queenside.  Black definitely has nice compensation with ... Be6 , ... Rfd8  and ...  Rac8  coming. }
