15. Bxe5( { It's worth pointing out that this exchange is completely justified if it allows Black to get complete control over the light squares on the queenside.    }15...b5?! { looks natural but after }16.Nxd7! Qxd7 17.a4!⩲ { Black has much more problems keeping their light-squared blockade intact. } )
