12. Nc6
13. Qb3( { Black could already repeat with }13...Na5 { but we have something much better. } )
13. Bc2{ Deflecting the queen. }
14. Qxc2
14. Qxb6{ Yes, we have given up the bishop pair but while White wasted moves with their knight, we developed our pieces. ... Nb4  and ... Rac8  comes quickly, ... Ne4  and ... Qa5  is an idea, even ... Nh5 , ... f6  and ... e5  can be strong.  White is in big danger. }
