13. Bf5( { The main idea behind this move is to go   }14...Qe6 { but }14...Nb4!? { can also be an idea to invade on the light squares. } )
14. h3{ This is a clever move to stop the ... Qe6  idea. Now, White is ready to play  g2 - g4  at a moment of their choice. }
14. Nb4{ Immediately trying to use the weak light squares. }
15. g4{ The only move to disturb Black's plan to invade with the knight. }
15. Bc2( { Black has to get in. }15...Bd7 { would lead to a position similar to   }14.g4 Bd7 { -  see here  - just that the ... Nb4  move doesn't make any sense in this setup. } )
