7. Ng1( { Other moves are not better.     A)  }7.Nd2 Qxd4-+ { loses the important central pawn. } )( {  B)  }7.Ne5 f6 { forks the minors. } )( {  C)  }7.Nh4 h6 { and ...  g5  traps the  h4 -knight. } )
