8. cxd4{ Black goes for a typical structure with hanging pawns. Usually, we have good versions of hanging pawn structures in the Grünfeld because our butcher on  g7  is ideally placed to put pressure on White's central pawns. }
9. exd4{ This is the typical way of recapturing. Taking with a piece is usually just considered super innocuous. }
