8. b3
8. c5{ Once again, this Grünfeld approach is extremely typical in these lines with  Nb1 - d2 . White has less central control, so we are very happy to increase the tension in the middle of the board. }
9. Bb2
9. b6{ The usual follow up is ... b6 , ... Bb7  and ... Rc8 . }
