11. Bxb5{ White has currently blocked the queenside quite nicely and for us, it is essential that we can mobilise our pawns. }
11. Na6{ A nice move. The knight can go to  c7  to attack the  b5 -bishop but it might also jump to  b4  and threaten to invade via the light squares. }
12. Bb2{ Ignoring Black's active ideas with this move gives Black an easy game. }
