11. bxa5( { White doesn't really have a better way to react. }11.b5 c5 { works nicely for us. } )
11. Rxa5{ Followed by ... Bb7 . Still, we will try to play for ... c5  at some point. The additional pressure along the a-file cannot be bad for us.  If White takes on  d5 , we recapture with the e-pawn to create further imbalances. }
