9. Nd2{ This is one of the engine's top moves. White forces Black to make a decision.  If Black takes on  c3 , which is the principled move to weaken White's pawn structure, White's knight supports both  c3 - c4  as well as  e3 - e4  at some point and also  Be2 - f3  is an idea. }
