13. Bg4{ This plays with the idea ... Bxf3  and also protects the  b8 -knight so that  Rb1  doesn't pin the  b4 -pawn. }( 13...c5 14.Rb1 Nc6 15.axb4 cxb4 16.Bd2⩲ { is leading to the same position that was mentioned on the last move. } )
