19. Bd3
20. Rfd1
20. Be2{ A nice in-between move, forcing the rook to  e1 . }
21. Re1
21. Bb5{ The c-pawn is so weak that Black can win it back at a moment of their choice. ... Bc3 , ... Rac8  look like good ways to start. Worst case, we always have ... Bxa4 . }
