4. g6{ We have covered all the important variations of the  e3 -Universe!     There are still a few very rare sidelines left, which I wanted to be included in the course but that are not worth a separate chapter and did not fit well into other chapters. So this short chapter is a "best of the rest."    There is not much to say, let's have a quick look! }
