16. Bd4
16. Nxe5{ With a decent position for Black. Black can try to mobilise their center pawns and just play ... h7 - h5 - h4  to soften White's kingside.  In Just - Tyulenko, Correspondence 2019, -  see here  - Black won a nice game after achieving both goals even though White made this easier than strictly necessary. }
