7. Bxb4( { This works tactically. }7...Bb6? 8.a5! axb5 9.axb6± { is what White is hoping for. There are some problems with the  a8 -rook and along the  f4 - b8  diagonal. } )
8. cxb4( { Necessary. The tempting }8.Nxc7+? { loses to }8...Qxc7! 9.Bxc7 Bxc3+-+ { when Black wins back the queen. } )
8. axb5
