22. Rc1{ The engine suggests that just sacrificing the c-pawn is White's best option. }( 22.c4 Nxc4 23.Nxc4 bxc4 24.Rc1 Be6∓ { Obviously, not an obvious decision. } )
22. b4{ A strong move, using the pin along the c-file. White is now losing material. }
