1. --{ To become an expert in an opening, you should know not only the typical plans but also the typical tactical motifs.     Each of the following positions is taken somewhere from the theory part of the course. Once you have internalized the following motifs, it will hopefully be even easier for you to learn the theoretical variations of the course.    But that was not the main reason why I wanted to include a tactics chapter: I think it is just fun! In this spirit, enjoy the chapter! }
